import React from "react"

import Header from "libs/components/molecules/Header"
import { Route, Router } from "react-router-dom"
import MainRoot from "libs/components/views/main"

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Header />
        <Route path="/" element={<MainRoot />} />
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
